  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/1a53bc6ff2f90d8675a112609491194d.poster.avif?t=1740111445\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/1a53bc6ff2f90d8675a112609491194d.webm?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/1a53bc6ff2f90d8675a112609491194d.mp4?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Embark on an epic ass-kicking, card-slinging journey across purgatory. Create your custom character, build your deck and do battle with the twisted enemies as you journey to the paradise you deserve. Cast spells, summon allies, and equip a variety of items and equipment as you explore what lies behind the Doors of Insanity. No sword is too big, no armor too thick, no ally too annoying!  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/6592c9fd8fa5def1b6d2238eb89eb335.poster.avif?t=1740111445\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/6592c9fd8fa5def1b6d2238eb89eb335.webm?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/6592c9fd8fa5def1b6d2238eb89eb335.mp4?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> <i>Improve your character between runs! Create a new god in the Realm of Madness! </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Collect and use over 90 cards! </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Summon stalwart allies including Shield Beaters, Wizards, and Demonic Bugs! </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Wield a variety of magical weapons including the powerful <strong>Sword Of The Three Saints</strong> and the substantially less-powerful <strong>Dad's Hammer</strong></i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Equip magical artifacts that change how you approach the game. Consume items with the <strong>Equipment Master</strong> set, summon the whole squad with the <strong>Summoner Master</strong> set, or rain down fiery combos with the <strong>Dice Master</strong> set!</i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Engage in dozens of encounters hidden behind the Doors of Insanity </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Travel through 4 huge areas each with their own enemies, encounters, and secrets</i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Join the developers as they work with the community to build the ultimate deck building roguelike </i> <br><br> </li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/c720d90199cd7b36dadf696d0d1c62fe.poster.avif?t=1740111445\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/c720d90199cd7b36dadf696d0d1c62fe.webm?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/c720d90199cd7b36dadf696d0d1c62fe.mp4?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/1a53bc6ff2f90d8675a112609491194d.poster.avif?t=1740111445\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/1a53bc6ff2f90d8675a112609491194d.webm?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/1a53bc6ff2f90d8675a112609491194d.mp4?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Embark on an epic ass-kicking, card-slinging journey across purgatory. Create your custom character, build your deck and do battle with the twisted enemies as you journey to the paradise you deserve. Cast spells, summon allies, and equip a variety of items and equipment as you explore what lies behind the Doors of Insanity. No sword is too big, no armor too thick, no ally too annoying!  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/6592c9fd8fa5def1b6d2238eb89eb335.poster.avif?t=1740111445\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/6592c9fd8fa5def1b6d2238eb89eb335.webm?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/6592c9fd8fa5def1b6d2238eb89eb335.mp4?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> <i>Improve your character between runs! Create a new god in the Realm of Madness! </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Collect and use over 90 cards! </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Summon stalwart allies including Shield Beaters, Wizards, and Demonic Bugs! </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Wield a variety of magical weapons including the powerful <strong>Sword Of The Three Saints</strong> and the substantially less-powerful <strong>Dad's Hammer</strong></i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Equip magical artifacts that change how you approach the game. Consume items with the <strong>Equipment Master</strong> set, summon the whole squad with the <strong>Summoner Master</strong> set, or rain down fiery combos with the <strong>Dice Master</strong> set!</i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Engage in dozens of encounters hidden behind the Doors of Insanity </i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Travel through 4 huge areas each with their own enemies, encounters, and secrets</i> <br><br></li><li> <i>Join the developers as they work with the community to build the ultimate deck building roguelike </i> <br><br> </li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/c720d90199cd7b36dadf696d0d1c62fe.poster.avif?t=1740111445\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/c720d90199cd7b36dadf696d0d1c62fe.webm?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268810/extras/c720d90199cd7b36dadf696d0d1c62fe.mp4?t=1740111445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
